{"tid":372785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［⋯］英國火警 18小豬獲救 被製成香腸答謝消防員","createTime":"2017-08-24T14:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T17:25:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa8b1400add16eedaec961c3474a23ec80ad516","tid":372785,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消防員拯救無數生命，有時救的還可能是小動物。英國有一批小豬逃得過火口，卻避不過刀鋒，成為了報答消防員的謝禮。<br />\n<br />\n美國《赫芬頓郵報》報道，英國皮尤西消防局在今年二月從一個穀倉大火中拯救了18隻小豬。半年後農場主人將這些小豬製成香腸，送給消防局當作謝禮。<br />\n<br />\n場主表示想感謝這些消防員，又指當時答應過消防員會送香腸給他們，他們聽到亦覺得開心。不過場主承認，這行為應該會引起素食者反感，但她認為這是農場的工作，不會把小豬當成寵物。<br />\n<br />\n消防局收到禮物後將香腸烤來吃，又將照片上載到社交網站，指他們可以在半年後品嚐到員工二月時的工作成果，這則帖文其後被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n消防當局亦回應指感謝場主的慷慨，並認為那些香腸非常美味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=233442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233442&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=dca90cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233442&h=d25b4a3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=233442</a>"},{"pid":"1ea231b9c8c4c7860cbda520da012f08c274799b","tid":372785,"uid":36321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:27:36.000Z","msg":"咁變左乳豬好似好食啲"},{"pid":"4621e655a42c51a6e0d47017fcb9bc8356a57438","tid":372785,"uid":56366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1519926eb3fdac76ab4da6a6f0df1d8e77378245","tid":372785,"uid":17901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【Now新聞台】消防員拯救無數生命，有時救的還可能是小動物。英國有一批小豬逃得過火口，卻